org.pwr.odwa.server.metadata
Class Meta

java.lang.Object
  org.pwr.odwa.server.metadata.Meta
Direct Known Subclasses:
Child, Dimension, Hierarchy, Level, Measure, Member
public class Meta
extends java.lang.Object

This is a base class for all metadata elements. This class provides a set of basic information about an metadata element, which includes the unique ID, user friendly name (non-unique), even more user friendly description (non-obligatory) and element type (mostly for internal purpose).
